  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this Prologue version of \"Express <i>Car Wash Simulator</i>\", you can experience the core gameplay mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wash, foam and relax. Feel the satisfying experience.  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> START WASHING!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy and intuitive mechanics </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Jump to the action straight away- </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wash cars with various colored soaps.. Feast for the eyes!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/1b83a6eaab479326bdc4fce7ee7c2bd1.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=618 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/1b83a6eaab479326bdc4fce7ee7c2bd1.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/1b83a6eaab479326bdc4fce7ee7c2bd1.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect cards and welcome new customers!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From small sedans to large SUVs and even trucks, wash a wide range of cars and earn money for each one you clean.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/7b07979a39442c79d2b27498514c235b.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/7b07979a39442c79d2b27498514c235b.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/7b07979a39442c79d2b27498514c235b.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Trust or Trouble?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some customers might seem harmless... but don’t be fooled, each one could be hiding something. Think twice before handing over the keys: Trust can lead to profit, or to trouble.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/c77ded7a63363eda7eee042d16b0d550.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/c77ded7a63363eda7eee042d16b0d550.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/c77ded7a63363eda7eee042d16b0d550.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make It Yours</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize each car with a variety of fun stickers: Add personality, flair, or just a bit of chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/917bdbf72afdc1f107e1310b2d1008a3.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/917bdbf72afdc1f107e1310b2d1008a3.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/917bdbf72afdc1f107e1310b2d1008a3.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wash cars with Colored Soaps ! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the satisfying sight of vibrant, colorful foam!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/80b0f24fbee36a824d237991f39e6d80.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/80b0f24fbee36a824d237991f39e6d80.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/80b0f24fbee36a824d237991f39e6d80.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/5238c632eb40b682c6e80e4053947887.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/5238c632eb40b682c6e80e4053947887.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/5238c632eb40b682c6e80e4053947887.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Care your customers!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't forget to satisfy your customers to maintain your business!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Their happiness is YOUR happine$$ </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/bc69a2d1ebfaceea86ed6b7feee17652.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/bc69a2d1ebfaceea86ed6b7feee17652.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/bc69a2d1ebfaceea86ed6b7feee17652.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/fb0bb9c0d9ac0b49bb80221d8adfac90.poster.avif?t=1767837964\" width=618 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/fb0bb9c0d9ac0b49bb80221d8adfac90.webm?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3156530/extras/fb0bb9c0d9ac0b49bb80221d8adfac90.mp4?t=1767837964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p>",
